## Required process

1. Analyze only; do not edit immediately.
2. Trace callers and contracts.
3. Identify migration, external-system, auth, or compatibility impact.
4. Produce an implementation plan.
5. Wait for human confirmation when required.
6. Implement minimally.
7. Run focused verification and request review.
